Trypanosomosis, Argentina
-------------------------
Information received on [and dated] 30 Jun 2017 from Dr Jorge Horacio Dillon, Presidente, Servicio Nacional de Sanidad y Calidad Agroalimentaria (SENASA), Ministerio de Agricultura, Ganader√≠a y Pesca, Buenos Aires, Argentina

Summary
Report type: Immediate notification
Date of start of the event: 7 Apr 2017
Date of confirmation of the event: 22 May 2017
Report date: 30 Jun 2017
Reason for notification: 1st occurrence of a listed disease
Manifestation of disease: clinical disease
Causal agent: _Trypanosoma vivax_
Nature of diagnosis: clinical, laboratory (basic and advanced)
This event pertains to the whole country

